{"id":232519667,"title":"湯頭秒殺㊙️新加坡豆漿魚片米粉","content":"正在減重的朋友絕對會愛上的料理\n愛吃火鍋這道100%也會愛上呀😻😻😻\n重點只要有卡式爐就能煮囉！\nhttps://i.imgur.com/wDjcIDO.jpg\n《8人份食譜》\n卡式爐開中火🔥🔥🔥\n❶ 熱鍋倒橄欖油（約70-80ml)\n❷ 洋蔥絲拌炒(一顆)+蝦米，炒到香氣出來\n❸ 胡蘿蔔絲(一根)拌炒一下\n❹ 鴻禧菇、雪白菇或白頭菇（一包）拌炒\n再轉大火🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥\n❺ 放入粗米粉一包 \n❻倒入1800cc微甜豆漿+些許水淹過米粉\n➡️可依個人喜好濃度調整（通常1：1）\n❼ 鯛魚片+青江菜，蓋鍋大火悶煮約15mins\n❽ 開鍋蓋放入3匙鹽巴+約一匙魚露\n⚠️因鍋子材質導熱屬性快慢不同，悶鍋時間不一定\n\n🌟Tips:一定要粗米粉，且要先浸泡水約10分鐘，口感才好吃\n————————————————\n最近剛辦一個異國料理日記的IG\n只要有卡式爐就能完成的料理，歡迎追蹤🍳\nhttps://www.instagram.com/mama_lovecooking/\nhttps://i.imgur.com/y4u8ddH.jpg","excerpt":"正在減重的朋友絕對會愛上的料理，愛吃火鍋這道100%也會愛上呀，重點只要有卡式爐就能煮囉！，《8人份食譜》卡式爐開中火，熱鍋倒橄欖油（約70-80ml），洋蔥絲拌炒（一顆）+蝦米，炒到香氣出來，胡蘿蔔","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d7db42a8-bedb-4ea2-96a7-c9034f4dd89a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-17T14:00:27.774Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-17T14:08:53.564Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":61,"tags":[],"topics":["食譜","烹飪","在家輕鬆做","蛋白質","減重"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"烹飪","forumAlias":"cooking","school":"國立高雄第一科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":61}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/wDjcIDO.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/y4u8ddH.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"1205a4ca-c52b-4e62-a3c8-662c0505b296","url":"https://i.imgur.com/wDjcIDOl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/wDjcIDOl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/wDjcIDOl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-17T14:00:27.774Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-17T14:08:53.564Z"},{"id":"1205a4ca-c52b-4e62-a3c8-662c0505b296","url":"https://i.imgur.com/wDjcIDO.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/wDjcIDO","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/wDjcIDOl.jpg","type":"image/